This is RhoStratego version 0.1.


Requirements:
  * gcc
  * gmake
  * xt-0.7
  * Stratego 0.5.4 with the following patch applied to list-misc.r:

*** list-misc-old.r     Sat Jul  7 21:51:17 2001
--- list-misc.r Sat Jul  7 21:55:30 2001
***************
*** 31,37 ****
    TFoldR   : TCons(x, xs) -> (x, xs)
 
    FoldL(s) : ([x | xs], y) -> (xs, <s> (x, y))
-   FoldL(s) : ([], y) -> y
 
    lsplit(f, g) : x -> [<f> x, <g> x]
 
--- 31,36 ----
***************
*** 49,55 ****
 
    tfoldr(s1, s2)    = rec x(TNil; s1 + TFoldR; (id, x); s2)
 
!   foldl(s) = repeat(FoldL(s))
 
    mapfoldr(s1, s2, s3) =
      rec x([]; s1 <+ [s2|x]; \ [a|b]->(a,b)\; s3)
--- 48,54 ----
 
    tfoldr(s1, s2)    = rec x(TNil; s1 + TFoldR; (id, x); s2)
 
!   foldl(s) = rec x( \ ([], y) -> y \ + FoldL(s); x)
 
    mapfoldr(s1, s2, s3) =
      rec x([]; s1 <+ [s2|x]; \ [a|b]->(a,b)\; s3)


To build:
  make


To test that the compiler works correctly:
  cd xmpl; make test
